articles.author: The Star Online
articles.title: Two Singapore club bosses who told dancers to have sex with customers jailed and fined - The Star Online
articles.description: SINGAPORE (The Straits Times/Asia News Network): A Bangladeshi woman came to Singapore thinking that an agent had arranged a domestic worker job for her, but was instead told to work as a dancer in a club.
